---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Max Burkhardt" description="Game development student at HvA with expertise in gameplay programming, level design, and AI systems.">
  <section class="container-narrow" style="padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-md) var(--spacing-xxl);">
    <div class="reveal">
      <h1 style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);">About Me</h1>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);">
        Game Developer & Designer
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);">
      <h2>Bio</h2>
      <p style="line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.0625rem;">
        I'm Max Burkhardt, a game development student at the Hogeschool van Amsterdam (HvA). 
        My passion lies in creating engaging gameplay experiences through responsive systems and thoughtful design. 
        I specialize in gameplay programming, level design, and AI implementation, with a focus on making 
        movement feel intuitive and combat satisfying.
      </p>
      <p style="line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.0625rem;">
        Throughout my projects, I've developed expertise in C# and Unity, working on everything from 
        character controllers to enemy AI behavior trees. I enjoy the challenge of balancing technical 
        implementation with player experience, always keeping the fun factor at the forefront.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);">
      <h2>Skills & Expertise</h2>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);">
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);">Programming</h3>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; color: var(--color-muted);">
            <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0;">• C# (Unity, MonoGame)</li>
            <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0;">• JavaScript / TypeScript</li>
            <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0;">• Git version control</li>
            <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0;">• Object-oriented design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);">Game Development</h3>
          <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; color: var(--color-muted);">
            <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0;">• Gameplay programming</li>
            <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0;">• Level design & spatial design</li>
            <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0;">• AI & behavior systems</li>
            <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0;">• Player experience design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);">
      <h2>Contact & Links</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">
        I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers and exploring new opportunities.
      </p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--spacing-md); flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">
        <a href="https://github.com/murkyperki" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn">
          GitHub Profile
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:max.burkhardt.burkhardt@hva.nl" class="btn btn-secondary">
          Email Me
        </a>
      </div>
      <a href="/CV.pdf" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">
        Download my CV (PDF) →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
